  <h2>Berlin &amp; Diaspora</h2>
  <p>Berlin has always been a city of arrivals. Berlindisch draws on that energy — the flavours, the hustle, the remixed traditions — and channels it into ventures and culture that feel honest. Culture moves through food, trade, and the things people build. Read more in our <a href="/manifesto/">manifesto</a>.</p>
